        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/skunk/scene_skunk.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository dff26cc7-ac07-4a50-a30d-b8917b7c4649).Image",
        "Description": "Finnaly, all of them, monsters, killers and even some from the police. I&apos;ve been waiting for all of them, now it is the time, now I will do what I must.\rI can&apos;t hold it any longer, I have to deal with one last thing before I can go live a &quot;normal life&quot; with Harrison, he lost too much, his mother, brother and sister, he can&apos;t lose a father.\rFinnaly there, I will deal with all of them at once:\r\r-Boyd Fowler\r-Arthur Mitchell\r-James Doakes\r-Travis Marshall\r-Hannah McKay\r\rI was never ment to be human",
        "GameVersion": "8.23.0.0",
